三、调用工具 (MCP Protocol)

请求：
POST /api/v2/mcp/pdooh/tools/call
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "工具名称",
  "arguments": {
    // 工具参数
  }
}

示例 1：查询智能屏点位
curl -X POST http://47.253.159.62:5002/api/v2/mcp/pdooh/tools/call \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "name": "pdooh_query_screens",
    "arguments": {
      "city": "广州",
      "district": "天河区",
      "min_house_price": 8,
      "limit": 10
    }
  }'

响应：
{
  "content": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "天河城社区门禁屏",
